# .chktexrc — ChkTeX configuration for Beamer/tcolorbox projects
#
# Suppresses false positives common in Beamer presentations
# with custom tcolorbox environments and TikZ diagrams.

# Suppress noisy warnings:
# 6:  No italic correction (\/') — not needed in modern LaTeX/Beamer
# 13: Intersentence spacing after periods (too aggressive for slides)
# 18: Straight quote marks (intentional in code/URLs)
# 31: \\[...] after tikzpicture (misinterpreted as text)
# 38: Punctuation in front of quotes — false positive with LaTeX ``...'' style
CmdLine { -n6 -n13 -n18 -n31 -n38 }

# Register custom tcolorbox environments as verbatim-like
# (prevents "unknown environment" warnings)
VerbEnvir { tikzpicture }
VerbEnvir { methodbox }
VerbEnvir { keybox }
VerbEnvir { highlightbox }
VerbEnvir { assumptionbox }
VerbEnvir { quotebox }
VerbEnvir { resultbox }
VerbEnvir { eqbox }
VerbEnvir { softbox }
